# Multiplayer RPG

Multiplayer RPG is an API for a new exciting multiplayer RPG.

## Users [/users/{playerID}]

### Retrieves a player's data with the score [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "userName":"halzate",
            "score": 900
        }

### Stores player's new score [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "score": 1000
        }

+ Response 200

## User leaderboard [/leaderboard/{playerID}]

### Retrieves a player's leaderboard position [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "position": 1
        }

## Global leaderboard [/leaderboard{?pageSize,page}]

### Retrives paged leaderboard starting from the first player [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id":"50AF87",
                "userName":"halzate",
                "score":900,
                "position":1
            },

            {
                "id":"51BF88",
                "userName":"rompeqkas",
                "score":750,
                "position":2
            },

            {
                "id":"52CF89",
                "userName":"smontes",
                "score":550,
                "position":3
            }
        ]

