## Character services [/character/{playerID}]

### Unlock character [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "type": "warrior",
            "element": "fire"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "type": "warrior",
            "level":1,
            "life": 500,
            "attack": 25,
            "defense": 20,
            "magicAttack": 5,
            "magicDefense": 5,
            "element": "fire"
        }

## Character stats services [/stats/{playerID}{?characterType,characterElement}]

### Add stats points [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "statToIncrease": "attack",
            "pointsToAdd": 5
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "type": "warrior",
            "level":1,
            "life": 500,
            "attack": 30,
            "defense": 20,
            "magicAttack": 5,
            "magicDefense": 5,
            "element": "fire"
        }

